sources.title: A Lawman Is Born 1937 (Western Movie) Johnny Mack Brown, Iris Meredith, Warner Richmond
sources.description:
In a world of outlaws and injustice, one man must confront his past to secure his future.
Tom Mitchell thought he left his outlaw days behind, but fate has other plans when he's appointed sheriff after the town's lawman is slain. As his past resurfaces, he's thrust into a deadly game of cat and mouse, fighting to prove his innocence and uphold justice in a lawless land.

Original title: A Lawman Is Born (1937)


Colorized version: https://youtu.be/cVSy2aMSGVg


This film is available with subtitles in many languages.
Director: Sam Newfield
Writers: Harry F. Olmsted, George H. Plympton
Actors: Johnny Mack Brown, Iris Meredith, Warner Richmond, Mary MacLaren, Dick Curtis
Genre: Classics, Western
